    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Movavi Slideshow Maker</strong></h2> 是一款简单却强大的工具，可帮助您将多媒体资源转换成极具吸引力的幻灯片。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>放飞您的想象力</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>上传所需的任何素材：度假照片、有趣的视频，甚至屏幕截图。程序会将您的文件保存在媒体区中，您可以随时轻松访问。<br></li><li>在蒙太奇表上移动多媒体，合并及修剪短片，使用改进的“裁剪和旋转”工具，垂直和水平镜像图像。<br></li><li>添加喜欢的曲目或使用内置声音和音乐。<br></li><li>还可从网络摄像机或外部设备添加旁白和录制图像。<br></li><li>通过标题和简介视频，您可以创建演职人员名单。<br></li><li>颜色选取器可帮助您选择出色的标题颜色。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/7684873c2704c8291f96d30e4eb26a09.poster.avif?t=1640598420\" width=500 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/7684873c2704c8291f96d30e4eb26a09.webm?t=1640598420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/7684873c2704c8291f96d30e4eb26a09.mp4?t=1640598420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>从幻灯片向导开始</strong></h2>如果您刚开始使用本程序，请尝试使用幻灯片向导。这是一种自动模式，可帮助您立即创建视频。您只需导入文件并选择主题。程序会瞬间创建演示文稿。您还可以设置目标视频长度和更改标题。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/5b169e3a539010903cd72923d558096c.poster.avif?t=1640598420\" width=500 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/5b169e3a539010903cd72923d558096c.webm?t=1640598420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/5b169e3a539010903cd72923d558096c.mp4?t=1640598420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>实现完美效果</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>应用过渡将短片与动画连接起来，让演示文稿流畅自然。<br></li><li>尝试放大和缩小图片，使用淡入淡出效果或使幻灯片滑过。<br></li><li>使用滤镜和特效惊艳观众。<br></li><li>让视频看起来像带晕影的复古电影一般。<br></li><li>移轴效果会将您的素材变成卡通风格的微缩影像。<br></li><li>借助各种效果和滤镜，您还可以锐化细节，减少相机抖动，并使图像更明亮、更丰富多彩。</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/aba2b0d3a6daec463b0ccdeedf0171f3.poster.avif?t=1640598420\" width=500 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/aba2b0d3a6daec463b0ccdeedf0171f3.webm?t=1640598420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/aba2b0d3a6daec463b0ccdeedf0171f3.mp4?t=1640598420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>尝试好莱坞风格</strong></h2>为您的视觉素材增添好莱坞风格并引入一些特效。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>使用色度键更改背景并将角色放置在完全不同的环境中。<br></li><li>使用“平移和缩放”工具添加动态元素。<br></li><li>慢动作会营造悬念，吊足观众的胃口。<br></li><li>如果要剪切掉包含特定角色的场景，可尝试“场景检测”。</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/e46e835747544ac408c72528e967ee91.poster.avif?t=1640598420\" width=500 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/e46e835747544ac408c72528e967ee91.webm?t=1640598420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/e46e835747544ac408c72528e967ee91.mp4?t=1640598420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>保存并展示</strong></h2>在演示文稿制作完成后，Movavi Slideshow 会将其保存在计算机上。选择一种流行格式，例如 AVI、MOV 或 MP4，或将素材直接传输到设备。还可与朋友共享视频，直接在程序内将其立即上传至 YouTube。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1242850/extras/f45d67e27e1905556e9f7ecd3e3a2